TEIform=\"foreign\">πρᾶγμα δεῦρ᾽ ἐπέσκηψεν</foreign> it <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">came to</tr_> this point, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg007.perseus-grc1:482\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eu.\">Eu.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">482</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νόσος ἐπέσκηψεν πολλή</foreign> (v.l.<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐν-</foreign>) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg001:15\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thes.\">Thes.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ᾧ</foreign> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἂν ἔρως ἐπισκήψῃ</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.767d</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">701c</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">αὐτῷ ὁ θάνατος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0671.tlg001:31:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Philum.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Ven.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">31.3</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense><sense n=\"II\" id=\"n40867.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\">. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">lay it upon</tr_> one to do a thing, c. dat. pers. et <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μοῖρ᾽ ἐπέσκηψε</foreign> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Πέρσαις πολέμους διέπειν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:gr